        <item>
            <title>2.0.2</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 13:41:16 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>40</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Window and session close now follows Safari/Chrome tab semantics: ⌘W closes the active session; ⇧⌘W and the red title-bar button always close the window.
- Closing the window with sessions still running silently hides it (use ⌘0 to bring it back) — no more "Sessions are Running" confirmation dialog.
- File menu reorganized: New Session, Open Folder, Close Session, Close Window — single, tidy list with no duplicate Close items.

### Bug Fixes
- Webview channel ID is now recovered from any incoming message, fixing rare cases where session metadata could not be persisted.
]]></description>
